                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.512/161: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé at Tangier</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Childs</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-05-04T23:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 4, 1942—11 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>84. Your despatch 656, March 3. Despatch 640 has not been received. Your revised
                    draft of <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire</hi> is approved on the understanding
                    that the original draft does not raise any question essential to the
                    Department’s consideration of the revised draft.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
